item.title: CVE-2018-7840|2024-08-05T06:37:59.645Z -- videoxpert -- videoxpert%20opscenter%20versions%20prior%20to%203.1
item.description: A Uncontrolled Search Path Element (CWE-427) vulnerability exists in VideoXpert OpsCenter versions prior to 3.1 which could allow an attacker to cause the system to call an incorrect DLL.
